  <description><![CDATA[<p>Brewster Mountain Lodge offers a traditional Canadian lodge style accommodation with great facilities and location.</p>
<p><span><strong><span style="color: #e23333;">Free night available when you book 7 or 14 nights</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong><em>(See added value section below)</em></strong></span></p>
<h2><span>Canadian lodge</span></h2>
<p>Offering log furnishings and western décor, historic photos from the Brewster family define the interior of the lodge. All rooms are decorated with handcrafted custom-made log furnishings.<span></span></p>
<h2><span>A Banff original</span></h2>
<p>The Brewster Family is proud to honour over a century of western traditions by providing guests with accommodation in the heart of downtown <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" target="_blank" title="Banff">Banff</a>.</p>
<h2><span>Location</span></h2>
<p><span>You will be situated just one block from the Banff Avenue and central downtown, the hotel is just steps away from excellent dining, shopping and nightlife.</span></p>]]></description>
